citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 pm - 2:30
pm on 12/17/2015.
The inspector rang the doorbell and called both numbers on file with no response.
